name: joint
description:
You can only roll a joint if you have a bud, due to this the joint will not be available on the primary market. All joints will be donated to the 420 first buyers of each edition of the 420 High Et Nunc Buds.

If you smoke a joint join us.

High Et Nunc is a project of 420 NFTs buds, each flower has its unique characteristics, there are several species, strains, high, and rarities.

When you collect one of our buttons, you will be participating and supporting a community of artists who appreciate THC and are lovers of resined flowers. All tezos collected in this project will be used to buy weed, when you also want to smoke weed just flip this NFT.
